FILE - Project Management Operations

This is the first drop-down menu found in the main Movieola titlebar.

To use this tool move the mouse cursor over the word "File" and press
the left mouse button. This will prompt a drop down menu window with
the following selections:

	New	Alt+N
	Open	Alt+O
	Save	Alt+S
	Save as...
	Notes
	Print	Alt+P
	Make tape >
	System...	Alt+Y
	Exit	Alt+Q
